      "comment": "WHITE HOT DREAMS (8) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 400m behind Divergence (23.42) in a Grade 6/MDN. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Should bounce back. WHERE'S TIMMY (2) had the drop on the lead early on but could only manage second, beaten one length (17.15) at Murray Bridge Straight in a Maiden over 300m. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Well placed and gets his chance. DREAMTIME MASTER (6) copped a check in the run and finished out of the placings when sixth (24.12) at this track over 400m in a Grade 6/MDN. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Can measure up this time. FATEFULLY (4) is worth a look over a shorter trip this time.",
